INSERT INTO
    ais_vessels (
    mmsi,imo_number,call_sign,name,ship_width,ship_length,ship_type,eta,draught,destination
   )
SELECT
    *
FROM
    UNNEST(
        $1::INT[],$2::INT[],$3::TEXT[],$4::TEXT[],$5::INT[],$6::INT[],$7::INT[],$8::TIMESTAMPTZ[],$9::INT[],$10::TEXT[]
    )
        ON CONFLICT (mmsi) DO UPDATE SET imo_number = EXCLUDED.imo_number,call_sign = EXCLUDED.call_sign,name = EXCLUDED.name,ship_width = EXCLUDED.ship_width,ship_length = EXCLUDED.ship_length,ship_type = EXCLUDED.ship_type,eta = EXCLUDED.eta,draught = EXCLUDED.draught,destination = EXCLUDED.destination
